Architecture: 3-LLM agentic pipeline. Layer 1 PLANNER decides which deterministic
git/GitHub tools to invoke. Layer 2 SYNTHESIZER writes the cited explanation prose. Layer
3 CRITIC (independent provider) grades the draft and may trigger one re-plan + re-
synthesis round.

Demo mode: Planner and Synthesizer use deterministic scripted responses (the actual
production code paths run unchanged -- only the LLM brain is canned for reliability).
Critic uses a recorded scripted response. Add --live to use the real Anthropic Claude
Haiku 4.5 instead.

